⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Rootless Man
node GDS · GDS · ⟦The Rootless Man:GDS:d9f558⟧

WHO   — The Rootless Man — owning nothing, wanting nothing
WHAT  — The cost of the skill: the parable that mastering everyone else's desire can hollow out your own.
WHERE — GDS · The Goods (2009)  Framework inputs: The Goods: Live Hard, Sell Hard (2009, dir. Neal Brennan, Gary Sanchez/Paramount Vantage); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film's heart is the price the closer pays, and the rootless man is that price.
HOW   — By being able to want everything for others and nothing for himself, until the lot and Ivy crack it open.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I can make you want what you don't need. The joke's on me: I forgot how to want what I do.

